Ace Nollywood actor, Femi Adebayo has given his verdict on the ongoing land sales promo by Abuja-based T.Pumpy Concept Limited, developers of T.Pumpy Estates. The year 2020 has welcomed Nigerians with open arms to a season of unlimited mouth-watering offers in the real estate sector and Femi Adebayo believes it is a life time opportunity for every Nigerian to say ‘good bye to landlord wahala’ and key into the ‘awoof offer’ in the nation’s power seat. Earlier, T.Pumpy Developers Concepts Limited, developers of T Pumpy Estates, with 22 housing estates spread across Abuja, the nation’s capital had announced slash of its 4/5 bedroom duplex land sales with massive discounts. The estate land, which is government approved, is located along the Airport Road, Abuja. Speaking on the development, the entertainer in a shot clip posted on his social media handles, said
He said the land is about 650sqm for 4 or 5 bedroom duplex or penthouse or can be used for 4-bedroom standard bungalow. Explaining in detail the new development, Mr, Adebayo said the market value of the land if N3m, however, the company is giving out 20 percent discount, which is N600,000 and 2,020 block, which is valued at N380,000. “Total value discount is N980,000 off 3,000,000 which is 2,020,000. Pay 2,020,000 the land is yours. “That means to say, T.Pumpy don make 2020 a year of jollification for all of us,” he said. The T-Pumpy Concept team have decades of providing industry-acclaimed off-site home designs and constructions. Whether you’re interested in a manufactured home or an innovative modular design, the T-Pumpy Concept team continues to deliver what home buyers are looking for in their new homes along with the quality construction they expect and deserve. Corporate Office address: No. 12, Monrovia Street, Off Aminu Kano Crescent, Wuse II district, Abuja
